-- BES Angola Says Sobrinho to Be Replaced by Guerra as Bank’s CEO
-- B y   H e n r i q u e   A l m e i d a
-- 2012-10-23T14:25:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-23/bes-angola-says-sobrinho-to-be-replaced-by-guerra-as-bank-s-ceo.html
Alvaro Sobrinho, chief executive
officer of the Angolan unit of  Banco Espirito Santo SA (BES) , will be
replaced by Rui Guerra, BES Angola said today.  Sobrinho will remain at BES Angola as chairman to
coordinate the bank’s strategic plan for the next five years, it
said in an e-mailed statement through its public relations firm
Lisbon Communication Office.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Henrique Almeida in Lisbon at 
